          <h2>Ketel One Bloody Mary</h2>

          <h3>Ingredients:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>1.5 oz Ketel One Vodka</li>
            <li>5 oz  Tomato Juice</li>
            <li>0.3 oz Fresh Lemon Juice</li>
